fatal: Unable to create 'C:/Development/git/.git/index.lock': File exists.
{noformat}
However, right clicking on the branch and clicking "Checkout xxxxxx" works perfectly.

When You type a tag message with a quote character " You'll get error message from git:

{{git -c diff.mnemonicprefix=false -c core.quotepath=false tag -a -m "This is a test" to show the error" myTag 0f00ffea8455094173fa2c041f5c5c020b6e3625}}
